    <string name="power_guidance_title">Power hardening guidance</string>
    <string name="power_guidance_message">To improve session reliability on Android TV:

1) Allow "Screen timeout permission" (WRITE_SETTINGS) so the app can temporarily extend timeout and restore it later.
2) Disable battery optimization for this app for better continuity.
3) If your TV supports a display timeout option, consider setting it to Never.

This is practical hardening guidance, not a guarantee for every app behavior.</string>
